{"tid":846730,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句 其實00後係真係On9","createTime":"2018-10-03T15:26:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T06:02:31.000Z","uid":139907,"like":81,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"fb1191b2e80f62bda4d8496e076674314e518cdb","tid":846730,"uid":139907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T15:26:03.000Z","msg":"玩埋d乜撚史萊姆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拍片放youtube用把死人雞仔聲講乜撚 好靚好好dook(即係督）<br />\n化學野黎 有乜好玩 舊時玩鬼口水都無佢地咁癡線 仲diy放格仔鋪拎黎賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講緊小學生<br />\n<br />\n然後就抖音 更加唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜撚野手指舞已經夠On9<br />\n指埋d扭身扭勢又乜乜柒柒既係想點撚樣 個鏡頭就轉黎轉去 眼都花鳩埋 其實有乜撚好玩<br />\n<br />\n同至少八成小學雞都好撚迷泡菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細細個就識走去睇演唱會 追星 買成千鳩銀張飛<br />\n<br />\n咁我寧願佢地打機啦 起碼都用到少少腦先<br />\n有無人可以話我知 新一代點解會演化到咁弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a436eb732f1af35e416b0b3129e095a0308bda","tid":846730,"uid":46871,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T22:20:48.000Z","msg":"慢慢教化佢地啦 屌佢地有咩用"},{"pid":"f3b63e6cd8eeabb8805e17416d76bfe4bdbb7bcc","tid":846730,"uid":190818,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T23:02:05.000Z","msg":"就快有第一車00後畢業出黎打工<br />\n人力資源顧問又有野寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4da3477ba2e35642bf0c26d0c2e70dc5c5050b","tid":846730,"uid":200686,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T00:06:58.000Z","msg":"仲有咩撚野支那新説唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj